text: +SupraDarky Truth is no channel ever matched Fox Kids. The big 3, Super Mario, Donkey Kong, Medabots, Mushrambo/Shinzo, Escaflowne, Card Captor Sakura, Sailor Moon, Magical Doremi, TMNT, Mon Colle Knights, nearly all Marvel series and Power Rangers.
author: Kirabochips

text: +roamer45 In France we were lucky enough to have almost the exact same Fox Kids as in the US, Haim Saban being French. Not to mention we also had Game One (1st videogame/otaku channel outside of Japan) and Mangas (80s and seinen anime). The late 90s / early 00s were quite something...
